            <content:encoded><![CDATA[<p>We're excited to announce <strong>Negarity Color</strong> ‚Äî a modern, extensible color manipulation library for PHP 8.3+.</p>
<h2 class="anchor anchorTargetStickyNavbar_Vzrq" id="what-is-negarity-color">What is Negarity Color?<a href="https://jalaljaberi.github.io/negarity-color/sv/blog/introducing-negarity-color#what-is-negarity-color" class="hash-link" aria-label="Direktl√§nk till What is Negarity Color?" title="Direktl√§nk till What is Negarity Color?" translate="no">‚Äã</a></h2>
<p>Negarity Color is a comprehensive PHP library designed to make working with colors simple, powerful, and flexible. Whether you're building web applications, image processing tools, or design systems, Negarity Color provides everything you need to work with colors effectively.</p>
<h2 class="anchor anchorTargetStickyNavbar_Vzrq" id="key-features">Key Features<a href="https://jalaljaberi.github.io/negarity-color/sv/blog/introducing-negarity-color#key-features" class="hash-link" aria-label="Direktl√§nk till Key Features" title="Direktl√§nk till Key Features" translate="no">‚Äã</a></h2>
<h3 class="anchor anchorTargetStickyNavbar_Vzrq" id="-multiple-color-spaces">üé® Multiple Color Spaces<a href="https://jalaljaberi.github.io/negarity-color/sv/blog/introducing-negarity-color#-multiple-color-spaces" class="hash-link" aria-label="Direktl√§nk till üé® Multiple Color Spaces" title="Direktl√§nk till üé® Multiple Color Spaces" translate="no">‚Äã</a></h3>
<p>Negarity Color supports <strong>10 color spaces</strong> out of the box:</p>
<ul>
<li class=""><strong>RGB/RGBA</strong> - For screen and web applications</li>
<li class=""><strong>HSL/HSLA</strong> - Intuitive color manipulation</li>
<li class=""><strong>HSV</strong> - Color pickers and graphics software</li>
<li class=""><strong>CMYK</strong> - Professional printing</li>
<li class=""><strong>Lab/LCh</strong> - Perceptually uniform color matching</li>
<li class=""><strong>XYZ</strong> - Color science and conversions</li>
<li class=""><strong>YCbCr</strong> - Video and image compression</li>
</ul>
<h3 class="anchor anchorTargetStickyNavbar_Vzrq" id="-seamless-conversions">üîÑ Seamless Conversions<a href="https://jalaljaberi.github.io/negarity-color/sv/blog/introducing-negarity-color#-seamless-conversions" class="hash-link" aria-label="Direktl√§nk till üîÑ Seamless Conversions" title="Direktl√§nk till üîÑ Seamless Conversions" translate="no">‚Äã</a></h3>
<p>Convert between any color space with a single method call:</p>
<div class="language-php codeBlockContainer_Ckt0 theme-code-block" style="--prism-color:#393A34;--prism-background-color:#f6f8fa"><div class="codeBlockContent_QJqH"><pre tabindex="0" class="prism-code language-php codeBlock_bY9V thin-scrollbar" style="color:#393A34;background-color:#f6f8fa"><code class="codeBlockLines_e6Vv"><span class="token-line" style="color:#393A34"><span class="token keyword" style="color:#00009f">use</span><span class="token plain"> </span><span class="token package">Negarity</span><span class="token package punctuation" style="color:#393A34">\</span><span class="token package">Color</span><span class="token package punctuation" style="color:#393A34">\</span><span class="token package">Color</span><span class="token punctuation" style="color:#393A34">;</span><span class="token plain"></span><br></span><span class="token-line" style="color:#393A34"><span class="token plain" style="display:inline-block"></span><br></span><span class="token-line" style="color:#393A34"><span class="token plain"></span><span class="token variable" style="color:#36acaa">$color</span><span class="token plain"> </span><span class="token operator" style="color:#393A34">=</span><span class="token plain"> </span><span class="token class-name static-context">Color</span><span class="token operator" style="color:#393A34">::</span><span class="token function" style="color:#d73a49">rgb</span><span class="token punctuation" style="color:#393A34">(</span><span class="token number" style="color:#36acaa">255</span><span class="token punctuation" style="color:#393A34">,</span><span class="token plain"> </span><span class="token number" style="color:#36acaa">100</span><span class="token punctuation" style="color:#393A34">,</span><span class="token plain"> </span><span class="token number" style="color:#36acaa">50</span><span class="token punctuation" style="color:#393A34">)</span><span class="token punctuation" style="color:#393A34">;</span><span class="token plain"></span><br></span><span class="token-line" style="color:#393A34"><span class="token plain"></span><span class="token variable" style="color:#36acaa">$hsl</span><span class="token plain"> </span><span class="token operator" style="color:#393A34">=</span><span class="token plain"> </span><span class="token variable" style="color:#36acaa">$color</span><span class="token operator" style="color:#393A34">-&gt;</span><span class="token function" style="color:#d73a49">toHSL</span><span class="token punctuation" style="color:#393A34">(</span><span class="token punctuation" style="color:#393A34">)</span><span class="token punctuation" style="color:#393A34">;</span><span class="token plain"></span><br></span><span class="token-line" style="color:#393A34"><span class="token plain"></span><span class="token variable" style="color:#36acaa">$cmyk</span><span class="token plain"> </span><span class="token operator" style="color:#393A34">=</span><span class="token plain"> </span><span class="token variable" style="color:#36acaa">$color</span><span class="token operator" style="color:#393A34">-&gt;</span><span class="token function" style="color:#d73a49">toCMYK</span><span class="token punctuation" style="color:#393A34">(</span><span class="token punctuation" style="color:#393A34">)</span><span class="token punctuation" style="color:#393A34">;</span><span class="token plain"></span><br></span><span class="token-line" style="color:#393A34"><span class="token plain"></span><span class="token variable" style="color:#36acaa">$lab</span><span class="token plain"> </span><span class="token operator" style="color:#393A34">=</span><span class="token plain"> </span><span class="token variable" style="color:#36acaa">$color</span><span class="token operator" style="color:#393A34">-&gt;</span><span class="token function" style="color:#d73a49">toLab</span><span class="token punctuation" style="color:#393A34">(</span><span class="token punctuation" style="color:#393A34">)</span><span class="token punctuation" style="color:#393A34">;</span><br></span></code></pre></div></div>
<h3 class="anchor anchorTargetStickyNavbar_Vzrq" id="-immutable-by-default">üéØ Immutable by Default<a href="https://jalaljaberi.github.io/negarity-color/sv/blog/introducing-negarity-color#-immutable-by-default" class="hash-link" aria-label="Direktl√§nk till üéØ Immutable by Default" title="Direktl√§nk till üéØ Immutable by Default" translate="no">‚Äã</a></h3>
