<div class="language-php codeBlockContainer_Ckt0 theme-code-block" style="--prism-color:#393A34;--prism-background-color:#f6f8fa"><div class="codeBlockContent_QJqH"><pre tabindex="0" class="prism-code language-php codeBlock_bY9V thin-scrollbar" style="color:#393A34;background-color:#f6f8fa"><code class="codeBlockLines_e6Vv"><span class="token-line" style="color:#393A34"><span class="token variable" style="color:#36acaa">$color</span><span class="token plain"> </span><span class="token operator" style="color:#393A34">=</span><span class="token plain"> </span><span class="token class-name static-context">Color</span><span class="token operator" style="color:#393A34">::</span><span class="token function" style="color:#d73a49">rgb</span><span class="token punctuation" style="color:#393A34">(</span><span class="token number" style="color:#36acaa">255</span><span class="token punctuation" style="color:#393A34">,</span><span class="token plain"> </span><span class="token number" style="color:#36acaa">100</span><span class="token punctuation" style="color:#393A34">,</span><span class="token plain"> </span><span class="token number" style="color:#36acaa">50</span><span class="token punctuation" style="color:#393A34">)</span><span class="token punctuation" style="color:#393A34">;</span><span class="token plain"></span><br></span><span class="token-line" style="color:#393A34"><span class="token plain"></span><span class="token variable" style="color:#36acaa">$modified</span><span class="token plain"> </span><span class="token operator" style="color:#393A34">=</span><span class="token plain"> </span><span class="token variable" style="color:#36acaa">$color</span><span class="token operator" style="color:#393A34">-&gt;</span><span class="token function" style="color:#d73a49">with</span><span class="token punctuation" style="color:#393A34">(</span><span class="token punctuation" style="color:#393A34">[</span><span class="token string single-quoted-string" style="color:#e3116c">'r'</span><span class="token plain"> </span><span class="token operator" style="color:#393A34">=&gt;</span><span class="token plain"> </span><span class="token number" style="color:#36acaa">200</span><span class="token punctuation" style="color:#393A34">]</span><span class="token punctuation" style="color:#393A34">)</span><span class="token punctuation" style="color:#393A34">;</span><span class="token plain"></span><br></span><span class="token-line" style="color:#393A34"><span class="token plain" style="display:inline-block"></span><br></span><span class="token-line" style="color:#393A34"><span class="token plain"></span><span class="token keyword" style="color:#00009f">echo</span><span class="token plain"> </span><span class="token variable" style="color:#36acaa">$color</span><span class="token punctuation" style="color:#393A34">;</span><span class="token plain"> </span><span class="token comment" style="color:#999988;font-style:italic">// Still "rgb(255, 100, 50)" - original unchanged</span><span class="token plain"></span><br></span><span class="token-line" style="color:#393A34"><span class="token plain"></span><span class="token keyword" style="color:#00009f">echo</span><span class="token plain"> </span><span class="token variable" style="color:#36acaa">$modified</span><span class="token punctuation" style="color:#393A34">;</span><span class="token plain"> </span><span class="token comment" style="color:#999988;font-style:italic">// "rgb(200, 100, 50)" - new instance</span><br></span></code></pre></div></div>
<h3 class="anchor anchorTargetStickyNavbar_Vzrq" id="-flexible-filter-system">üé≠ Flexible Filter System<a href="https://jalaljaberi.github.io/negarity-color/sv/blog/introducing-negarity-color#-flexible-filter-system" class="hash-link" aria-label="Direktl√§nk till üé≠ Flexible Filter System" title="Direktl√§nk till üé≠ Flexible Filter System" translate="no">‚Äã</a></h3>
<p>Apply color transformations with a powerful filter system:</p>
<div class="language-php codeBlockContainer_Ckt0 theme-code-block" style="--prism-color:#393A34;--prism-background-color:#f6f8fa"><div class="codeBlockContent_QJqH"><pre tabindex="0" class="prism-code language-php codeBlock_bY9V thin-scrollbar" style="color:#393A34;background-color:#f6f8fa"><code class="codeBlockLines_e6Vv"><span class="token-line" style="color:#393A34"><span class="token keyword" style="color:#00009f">use</span><span class="token plain"> </span><span class="token package">Negarity</span><span class="token package punctuation" style="color:#393A34">\</span><span class="token package">Color</span><span class="token package punctuation" style="color:#393A34">\</span><span class="token package">Filter</span><span class="token package punctuation" style="color:#393A34">\</span><span class="token package">FilterRegistry</span><span class="token punctuation" style="color:#393A34">;</span><span class="token plain"></span><br></span><span class="token-line" style="color:#393A34"><span class="token plain"></span><span class="token keyword" style="color:#00009f">use</span><span class="token plain"> </span><span class="token package">Negarity</span><span class="token package punctuation" style="color:#393A34">\</span><span class="token package">Color</span><span class="token package punctuation" style="color:#393A34">\</span><span class="token package">Filter</span><span class="token package punctuation" style="color:#393A34">\</span><span class="token package">Parameterized</span><span class="token package punctuation" style="color:#393A34">\</span><span class="token package">BrightnessFilter</span><span class="token punctuation" style="color:#393A34">;</span><span class="token plain"></span><br></span><span class="token-line" style="color:#393A34"><span class="token plain"></span><span class="token keyword" style="color:#00009f">use</span><span class="token plain"> </span><span class="token package">Negarity</span><span class="token package punctuation" style="color:#393A34">\</span><span class="token package">Color</span><span class="token package punctuation" style="color:#393A34">\</span><span class="token package">Filter</span><span class="token package punctuation" style="color:#393A34">\</span><span class="token package">Unary</span><span class="token package punctuation" style="color:#393A34">\</span><span class="token package">InvertFilter</span><span class="token punctuation" style="color:#393A34">;</span><span class="token plain"></span><br></span><span class="token-line" style="color:#393A34"><span class="token plain" style="display:inline-block"></span><br></span><span class="token-line" style="color:#393A34"><span class="token plain"></span><span class="token class-name static-context">FilterRegistry</span><span class="token operator" style="color:#393A34">::</span><span class="token function" style="color:#d73a49">register</span><span class="token punctuation" style="color:#393A34">(</span><span class="token keyword" style="color:#00009f">new</span><span class="token plain"> </span><span class="token class-name">BrightnessFilter</span><span class="token punctuation" style="color:#393A34">(</span><span class="token punctuation" style="color:#393A34">)</span><span class="token punctuation" style="color:#393A34">)</span><span class="token punctuation" style="color:#393A34">;</span><span class="token plain"></span><br></span><span class="token-line" style="color:#393A34"><span class="token plain"></span><span class="token class-name static-context">FilterRegistry</span><span class="token operator" style="color:#393A34">::</span><span class="token function" style="color:#d73a49">register</span><span class="token punctuation" style="color:#393A34">(</span><span class="token keyword" style="color:#00009f">new</span><span class="token plain"> </span><span class="token class-name">InvertFilter</span><span class="token punctuation" style="color:#393A34">(</span><span class="token punctuation" style="color:#393A34">)</span><span class="token punctuation" style="color:#393A34">)</span><span class="token punctuation" style="color:#393A34">;</span><span class="token plain"></span><br></span><span class="token-line" style="color:#393A34"><span class="token plain" style="display:inline-block"></span><br></span><span class="token-line" style="color:#393A34"><span class="token plain"></span><span class="token variable" style="color:#36acaa">$color</span><span class="token plain"> </span><span class="token operator" style="color:#393A34">=</span><span class="token plain"> </span><span class="token class-name static-context">Color</span><span class="token operator" style="color:#393A34">::</span><span class="token function" style="color:#d73a49">rgb</span><span class="token punctuation" style="color:#393A34">(</span><span class="token number" style="color:#36acaa">255</span><span class="token punctuation" style="color:#393A34">,</span><span class="token plain"> </span><span class="token number" style="color:#36acaa">100</span><span class="token punctuation" style="color:#393A34">,</span><span class="token plain"> </span><span class="token number" style="color:#36acaa">50</span><span class="token punctuation" style="color:#393A34">)</span><span class="token plain"></span><br></span><span class="token-line" style="color:#393A34"><span class="token plain">    </span><span class="token operator" style="color:#393A34">-&gt;</span><span class="token function" style="color:#d73a49">brightness</span><span class="token punctuation" style="color:#393A34">(</span><span class="token number" style="color:#36acaa">20</span><span class="token punctuation" style="color:#393A34">)</span><span class="token plain"></span><br></span><span class="token-line" style="color:#393A34"><span class="token plain">    </span><span class="token operator" style="color:#393A34">-&gt;</span><span class="token function" style="color:#d73a49">invert</span><span class="token punctuation" style="color:#393A34">(</span><span class="token punctuation" style="color:#393A34">)</span><span class="token punctuation" style="color:#393A34">;</span><br></span></code></pre></div></div>
<h3 class="anchor anchorTargetStickyNavbar_Vzrq" id="Ô∏è-named-colors">üè∑Ô∏è Named Colors<a href="https://jalaljaberi.github.io/negarity-color/sv/blog/introducing-negarity-color#%EF%B8%8F-named-colors" class="hash-link" aria-label="Direktl√§nk till üè∑Ô∏è Named Colors" title="Direktl√§nk till üè∑Ô∏è Named Colors" translate="no">‚Äã</a></h3>
